<td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucylok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>cylok</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 1:11:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> Hunter's Pike<br>MAGIC ITEM  LORE ITEM  NO DROP<br>Skill: PIERCING   Atk Delay: 30<br>DMG: 12   WT: 8.5   Dmg/Sec: 8.33<br>AC+5  STR+3  CHA+2  <br>Class: WAR RNG SHD BRD ROG SHM BST <br>Race: ALL  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=shamah>Shamah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 1:54:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> I'd say no, personally for two reasons<br><br>first, It's a good BSer, but BS (until low 50's, someone correct me if I'm wrong) is only a very small portion of your damage output, so you shouldn't be thinking only BS.  Unless of course, you're looking for highest BS bragging rights.<br><br>Second,  it's heavy.  Comparatively, very heavy.  Me, I'd rather have something like an SBD (weighing in at around 2) and save the other 6 weight for cash and loot.  But then, I'm really big on making cash off what I kill, cause this is my only character, and mob's are the only place I get money. <br><br>But, there's my 2pp for ya.<br><!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Shamah <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uaphyd.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aphyd</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 2:43:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> It's a decent backstabber, but you would be better off with something with a nicer ratio.<br><br>Maybe go for that 10/25 piercer from Sebilis (i forgot the name, sue me)<br><br>Also, Shaded Dagger is nice if you want to save up some money.<br><br>I think it's selling for around 2-3k on my server now.<br><br>Shaded Dagge<br>11/22<br>+5 magic, cold, disease, poison, -5 sav fire<br>Piercing <p>Aphyd Pebble<BR><img src=http://xorthos.homestead.com/files/MyBadLuck.gif></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=makabrei>Makabrei</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 3:25:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> Crystaline spider fang is nice too. 10/22 +3 str procs vel shards. They are decent little pokers im very fond of mine. =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uyalum.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yalum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 4:40:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=4>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> I'd take 12/30 over 10/25, the extra backstab damage ought to make up for the higher delay, especially at the levels we're likely talking about.  The pike is a decent weapon and relatively easy to get, too. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/useiffel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>seiffel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 5:07:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> Decent backstab damage yes, but in general really slow on attacking.  I'd say go slime coated harpoon, crystalline spider fang, or trak tooth honestly.  Backstabs are part of your damage, but not all of it, being able to be hitting quite a few times in between backstabs is more valuable then being able to have a really high damage piercer, considering you have a chance to hit high backstabs, but the number of times you actually hit that higher max is still not going to be as high as you think, I hit my minimum more often during a fight then a really high backstab, just something to take into consideration. <p>Seiffil60 AssassinVeeshan</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uyalum.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yalum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 5:34:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> 10/25 and 12/30 are exactly the same ratio.  Discounting the damage bonus and backstab (offhand, for instance), they do <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> exactly the same damage</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  So the question is, does an extra backstab make up for the lost damage bonus on your mainhand?  Depends on your level, but the anwser is generally going to be yes.<br><br>Faster is not always better. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukileitheredeemed.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kilei the Redeemed</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 6:23:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> The biggest prob i've seen with heavy piercers is that bc of the high hit rate of rogues and our naturally low sta (usually) you will be running out of sta very quickly. That can be an extra annoyance, while fixable, isn't one i like to have to worry about when you can still find other comprable piercers with less weight. <p><img src="http://www.dragonoverlord.com/kflallsig.jpg" border="0"></a> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udrummondairsekikker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Drummond Airsekikker</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 11:39:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> I recently got a Slime Covered Harpoon from a shammy who had gotten a better weapon and I love it... wont trade it out until I get my epic I think or a Bloodpoint. I'm 31, I have lots of time LOL<br><br>It is quite heavy which means your Dex would have to be pretty high to get decent hits with it as well as a perma STR buff.  Personally, I would go for something a tad lighter. <p>Drummond Airsekikker<BR>Rogue of the 29th Season<BR>Guild Leader - Battle Forged<BR>Backstabber Extraordinaire<BR>"Excuse me, but that's my dagger in your back."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udaezbwa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DaezBwA</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 5:03:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> back in my day... we switched weapons out for backstabs... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>I would use the 12/30 one. especially if you are hasted. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unimmbull.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nimmbull</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/10/02 5:20:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> funny you mention it, this weapon was on a vendor- a friend bought it and at level 51 am hot-swapping it with my blood point when I feel like it.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Nimm <p>Nimmbull<br>Perennial Lowbie Rogue of <a href="http://pub52.ezboard.com/bwarcry97210">Cry of War</a><br><I><B>"Once a Blade, always a Blade."</I></B></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucylok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>cylok</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/13/02 12:56:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22184.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Good rogue weapon?</span><hr size=1> This weapon could not have been purcased from a vendor. It's nodrop and the result of a quest.<br> <p>Nebene